Setup:
Activate virtual environment
	virtualenv -p python3.7 .env
	. .env/bin/activate

Install punctuator
	pip install punctuator

Download punctuator models:
	gdown https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B7BsN5f2F1fZd1Q0aXlrUDhDbnM

	gdown https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7BsN5f2F1fZZ2ZXd3R0dEh6NDA/view?usp=sharing

If links dont work above, go to: 
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B7BsN5f2F1fZQnFsbzJ3TWxxMms



Using punctuator2.py:
	python punctuator2.py [textfile]

The two different models are as follows:
1. Demo-Europarl-En.pcl
2. INTERSPEECH-T-BRNN.pcl

Select the model after running python script

Notes:
	Works best when the entire document is lowercased
	Removes all filler words (uh)

